name: TAKE OFF
description:
Journal #001

As a child I always looked at the stars. Terrifying, fascinating.
I wanted to touch them, to be among them.
For many years it was just a child's dream.
Looking back, I see the cosmodrome getting smaller. I look forward to infinity.
The time has come.

Am I still dreaming?



_____
Soundtrack: Analog Moog synthesizer plus effects.
Video: 1080x1080px, H.264, 24fps.
